author: COMSOL
description: This tutorial shows how to simulate coupled heat and moisture transport in a 2D wood-frame wall, in order to evaluate the risk of condensation inside the wall. Different design and modeling approaches are compared under stationary outdoor conditions. In addition, the effect of the diurnal variation of outdoor humidity on the humidity distribution in the wall is computed.
